♪ How far away ♪

02:01:05.216 --> 02:01:09.386
♪ Little Rock, ARK ♪

02:01:09.471 --> 02:01:11.639
♪ Princeton, NJ ♪

02:01:11.765 --> 02:01:16.435
♪ How far are they ♪
